&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;b3.&lt;/b&gt; Uv.13.12a-b &lt;i&gt;alpajñāto ’pi ced bhavati śīleṣu susamāhitaḥ&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
